{"tid":1454354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【G20 x 攬炒團隊眾籌進度公告】","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:42:31.000Z","uid":50983,"like":570,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":143,"replies":[{"pid":"b71c5b5947d299adc64741967f8c4d735dfed9a3","tid":1454354,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"是次眾籌項目經發佈後，僅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩小時</span></strong>就已經完成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一百萬美元</span></span></strong>的眾籌目標，並達到<ins>原定目標近兩倍的款項</ins>，折合共<strong>約一千五百萬港元</strong>。我們謹此感激各位港人對我們團隊的信任和支持。<br />\n<br />\n目前所籌得的款額已暫時足夠我們應用，<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾籌平台亦已停止募捐</span></ins></strong>。如有進一步的需要，我們會再向廣大市民募資。請各位熱心市民切勿誤信其它假借我們旗號作招徠的眾籌，我們G20 x 攬炒團隊只此一家，集資階段亦已告結束。<br />\n<br />\n我們很清楚，能夠比上一次更快籌集到更多資金的原因並不在我們自身的號召力，而是政府再三激起全體市民忿恨所致。因此，我們定當妥善運用這筆資金，不負大家所託。當登報事宜全數結束後，我們會亦會公佈審計報告，明細各項結餘，請各位繼續留意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n另外，請恕眾籌團隊暫時無法接受傳媒採訪。現時團隊全數成員均密鑼緊鼓籌備眾籌事項中，未能抽身接受訪問，還望記者朋友們見諒。歡迎大家留下提問及聯絡方法，我們會於稍後完成眾籌項目後，盡快與各位聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n大家若有興趣跟進是次眾籌發展或提供相關資料，請加入 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/CuWe1xeIxUffvh9xR1qaZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FCuWe1xeIxUffvh9xR1qaZw&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a2b34676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/CuWe1xeIxUffvh9xR1qaZw</a> 。<br />\n<br />\n同時，歡迎大家留意我們的官方資訊台：<br />\n<br />\n官方眾籌頁面： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/standwithhk-international\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fstandwithhk-international&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=48c76ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/standwithhk-international</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial%2F&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=cdde5267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2F&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4bac6100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram Channel： <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFreedomHKG&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=d107e996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter： <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=f45fab09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=dbe5e5bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=1e66a27b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_%2F&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=f8d0d396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/</a><br />\n<br />\n容我們在最後再次感謝所有港人。"},{"pid":"9890901dcffb41269e3ce739f6bafa2794e17578","tid":1454354,"uid":50983,"like":150,"dislike":0,"score":150,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"201